&lt;p&gt;Band 5 Staff Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Medical Outpatient Department&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hull Royal Infirmary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The medical Outpatient Department at Hull Royal Infirmary have a vacancy for an enthusiastic, motivated staff nurse who is committed to delivery high standards of quality driven care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be required to support patients attending clinic with chronic and acute illness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yo will have excellent communication skills and a desire to work within a well established multidisciplinary team delivering a co-ordinated approach to patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be willing to undertake further training as part of their professional development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jane Wride jane.wride@hey.nhs.uk 01482 675589&lt;/p&gt;
